le=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px">论坛展示：论坛首页通过展示推荐帖，置顶帖，最新帖等，吸引用户眼球。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><img src="http://upload.opensns.cn/Uploads_Editor_Picture_2015-09-18_55fba8693d562.jpg" title="undefined"/><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px">板块展示：设置不同类型的版块，直观的展示方式，一目了然。</span></p><p><img src="http://upload.opensns.cn/Uploads_Editor_Picture_2015-09-18_55fba86c7d425.jpg" title="undefined"/><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px">帖子展示：了解每个版块内的热门贴和最新贴，可</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px; rgb(255, 255, 255)">自由地发帖或跟帖，与其他会员分享或交流。</span></p><p><img src="http://upload.opensns.cn/Uploads_Editor_Picture_2015-09-18_55fba86d68e58.jpg" title="undefined"/><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><img src="http://upload.opensns.cn/Uploads_Editor_Picture_2015-09-18_55fba86eb155d.jpg" title="undefined"/><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px">帖子管理：版主或管理员，可对版块内的帖子进行管理，置顶、编辑、评论、删除等。</span></p><p><img src="http://upload.opensns.cn/Uploads_Editor_Picture_2015-09-18_55fba87104deb.jpg" title="undefined"/><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>";s:5:"cover";s:3:"619";s:3:"uid";s:1:"1";s:4:"rate";s:1:"0";s:10:"view_count";s:1:"0";s:7:"type_id";s:2:"12";s:11:"create_time";s:10:"1432102414";s:11:"update_time";s:10:"1444705392";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"entity";s:1:"2";s:6:"author";s:36:"嘉兴想天信息科技有限公司";s:5:"sales";s:1:"0";s:11:"watch_count";s:2:"40";s:2:"ad";s:0:"";s:8:"need_buy";s:1:"0";s: